description: Winner of the 2010, 2011, and 2013 Burger Battle, Bite Gastrotruck is bringing quantifiable quality to the streets of Southern Florida. Offering one of one of America's top 100 burgers, with a large array of toppings, as well as crafted milkshakes, hand cut fries and onion rings, this truck will leave you full and happy no matter what your tastes. Check them out today!
name: Bite Gastrotruck
